data.description: Maintenance free living in gated community. Well maintained 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 1 car garage + loft overlooking community amenities. Features include open floor plan, half bath downstairs, ceiling fans, recessed lighting, 18x18 tile in wet areas, storage closets, laundry upstairs, split bedrooms, and large loft/flex space. Kitchen boasts 42" upper cabinets, stainless steel fridge and closet pantry. The primary suite offers double closets and an en suite bath with an oversized walk-in shower and dual sinks with a make up/vanity space in between. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle as you enter the backyard through sliding glass doors and enjoy privacy fencing on either side with NO REAR NEIGHBORS, while enjoying the view of the park. Just around the corner from the community amenities you are steps to the pool and picnic area, playground and open park areas. Located in the community of Hawk's Point you are walking distance to the local high school and elementary school. There are also 2 K-8 charter schools very nearby. Conveniently between US Hwy 41 and I-75 you have easy access to the roadways that will take you to Tampa, St Petersburg and Sarasota.
